{
  "stem": "6052.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, again, I might be off by the years, because I cannot be too exact.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he established.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were a kind of a helpful organization to people who were in need, and especially to children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they showed their proficiency when they did what they did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because this was the first time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They helped me the second time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- when I came back to Leipzig for one night from Hachshara, they helped me again, with this other small group, to escape from Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But coming back to Leipzig, to-- to my young children, to my children's year, there were things which are-- were very impressive on me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I could not really reconcile that such cultural place, with such cultural background-- and there was a cultural background-- Goethe, Schiller, and the monuments and all this-- could really reach the deepest, deepest, agonizing place in history of Jews when they did what they did to Jews.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They express the hatred.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We could not go anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And these rules came about, and I read about, and I knew about when my mother wrote me that they cannot go anymore to the public park, which was the-- closed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Forbidden to Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They could not go anymore to the movies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We could not go-- we could not go anymore to any public event!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And even-- And when the war broke out, in 1939, we could not go to the shelters anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I witnessed it, because I came back, and this one day when I came back, a bombardment occurred, and we could not go to the shelter.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Jews had to stay in their apartments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we are at risk, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I escaped-- now I'm coming to the part without finishing the other part.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
